<h2>Your Bevgo seller account has been blocked</h2>

<p>Hi <%= vendorName %>,</p>

<p>
Your seller account on Bevgo has been blocked pending a review.
</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Vendor:</strong> <%= vendorName %></li>
  <li><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= reasonLabel %></li>
  <% if (reasonMessage) { %>
    <li><strong>Details:</strong> <%= reasonMessage %></li>
  <% } %>
  <li><strong>Fix:</strong> <%= fixHint %></li>
</ul>

<p>
Once you have fixed the issue, open your seller dashboard and request a review.
</p>

<p style="margin-top: 20px;">
Cheers,<br/>
The Bevgo Team
</p>
